[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "嗨～尤蒂爾。最近過得好嗎？你最敬愛的姊姊為你帶來一則好消息囉。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "1000年前，有種武器在人類與龍族仍互相爭鬥的年代裡相當活躍，而時至今日，居然由我們香捷里亞傾盡全力將它重現於世了。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "我想說機會難得，就也分一些給你吧。你大可含淚向我這個溫柔的姊姊大人道謝喔！喔──呵呵呵呵呵呵！", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "這就是她說的武器……「銃」嗎。古代的武器啊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "嗯，但1000年前是技術能力遠比現代發達的年代。所以這絕對會是個強力的武器。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "雖然要使用被視為禁忌的武器，心情還蠻複雜的……但今後的戰鬥還會越來越激烈，所以一定會有幫助。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "我覺得謝斯姊姊也是看準這點，才會把這個轉讓給我們。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "呼，我聽說你的姊姊是個不近人情的女人，但這不是還挺親切的嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "……這個嘛，畢竟是謝斯姊姊，所以事情絕對不會這麼單純。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "以姊姊的個性來說，想必是希望得到更多銃的情報吧。而在這裡用於實戰的機會也比較多。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "哈，所以我們就是適合的實驗動物囉？然後呢？你告訴我這些就表示……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1015.wav"], "content": "如果喬你不介意的話，我希望你能用看看這把銃。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "雖然我知道被叫來當實驗對象，基本上是不會太高興啦……但我想聽聽擅長射擊的人有什麼心得。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "真服了你，被直接指名的話，我很難回絕耶。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "但是，我擅長的武器是弓箭。「銃」能不能和弓一樣得心應手，得要試了才知道囉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "那部分我並不擔心喔，你就收下它吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "非常順手……這感覺真奇妙。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾，你已經試用過這東西了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1001.wav"], "content": "就一下而已。所以才覺得，這個武器應該很適合喬。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "你很懂嘛。我也是拿起它的瞬間，直覺就告訴我了──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0068.wav"], "content": "這傢伙會帶給我新的刺激……我無法不這麼想。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "你感到滿意那就太好了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "那把「銃」，是將挖掘到的古代遺物復原後並加以改良的產物，目前似乎還沒有計畫要另外增產。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "好像說有個零件是儲存瑪納的汽缸，那部分沒有辦法複製出來──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "那種繁瑣的事情就別說了。重點就是這玩意很稀有對吧？我會謹慎使用，不弄丟也不弄壞它的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "過陣子我會再來找你，聽聽你的使用心得是如何。在那之前，你就自由地用它來射擊吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "嗯，交給我吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "被發掘的古代兵器……「銃」嗎。有趣，讓我整個興奮起來了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "我一定馬上就能駕馭它。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "哼，今天起我就從「手持爆炎弓的男人」變成「手持古代兵器──銃的男人」啦！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110003021, "title": "嶄新的可能性"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "呼，大致上已經熟悉了。但是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "狀況如何啊？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "是尤蒂爾啊。狀況大概算是不好也不壞吧。銃比我原本所想的還要深奧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "既然你都來了，要不要看看呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "看看？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "簡單的試射啦。我會瞄準你指的樹射擊，你就照喜好來選吧，多選幾棵也行。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "原來如此。那麼……稍微遠一點的那棵樹，還有那邊那根凸出來的樹枝如何？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "兩個目標嗎……那樹枝還真細啊。嗯唔，這看起來蠻難的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "不過，我就試試看吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "喝！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "……嘖，馬馬虎虎而已。但是，應該有打中你指定的目標喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯，這快速射擊真厲害！動作實在過於迅速，看起來就像只射了一發子彈而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "而且我指出來的兩個目標你也都打穿了……這樣的結果你還是覺得馬馬虎虎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "這只要稍微訓練，誰都能辦到……原本以為是我的話，可以射得更快、更準確的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "我覺得就算有長期訓練，也不是誰都能射得這麼快就是了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，曾經是我宿敵的那個男人，一定也可以辦到同樣……不，他一定能使出更高超的快速射擊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "喬的宿敵？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "我沒跟你說過嗎？曾經有個男人，為了在弓箭的世界裡與我爭奪最強男人的稱號，因而與我決鬥了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "呵……話題偏離得相當遠呢。不過，誰都能辦到這種話，或許是說得有點太誇張了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "但是，銃確實是誰都可以使用，比起其他武器要來得容易上手。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0081.wav"], "content": "譬如發射弓箭時就需要足夠的力量。就只有受過訓練的人才能射中遠方目標的。但是──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "要在實戰中使用銃，不須像在實戰中使用弓箭那樣受扎實的訓練。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "是這樣嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "嗯，銃所需要的動作就只有調整姿勢、瞄準、射擊……僅此而已。這三個動作都不需要用力。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "由銃所擊出的瑪納，也是將原本就注入子彈中的瑪納射出而已，所以對使用者來說一點負擔也沒有。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "不管是誰來使用銃，只要扣下扳機就能有相當強的威力。只是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "……有什麼讓你介意的事嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，我自己也還沒有完整掌握它……銃是非常優秀的武器，讓我愛不釋手。但是，內心的某處還是有著一抹不安。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "所以尤蒂爾……不好意思，這把銃能不能再借我多用一段時間呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1015.wav"], "content": "嗯，沒問題喔。本來就是為了要徹底了解它的用法才讓你試用的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "呵，感謝你了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "既然都這麼決定了……那麼你要不要稍微幫我試射一下呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "你說幫忙，實際要做些什麼才好呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "我會把蘋果放在頭上，然後你試著將它給打下來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "是由我來射嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "呵，我開玩笑的啦。萬一到時候我的腦袋被打穿了，可就笑不出來咧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "當我第一次拿到這玩意時，直覺地感受到獲得嶄新刺激的可能性……我一定會徹底掌握它。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110003022, "title": "愛不釋手與一抹不安"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "大致就是這樣了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "這樣一來，這一帶的魔獸基本上應該就都打倒了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "真厲害啊，喬！你已經把銃使用得淋漓盡致了啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "是尤蒂爾啊。你那邊看來也收拾得差不多了呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯。這樣一來危害村莊的魔獸應該就全部都擊退了……這也都多虧了喬使用銃的高超技巧喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "所以，之前你提過讓你在意的事情，已經弄清楚原因了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "呵，托你的福囉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "雖然我中途開始就沒再繼續數下去了，不過我已經用這把銃擊倒一百隻以上的魔獸……但還是不夠。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1003.wav"], "content": "你說的不夠是指什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "刺激啊。用銃將敵人打倒時的刺激感──也就是打倒敵人的真實感不夠。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "那部分……也是，對喬來說或許非常重要呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "不是的，尤蒂爾。這並不單純是我這種想在戰鬥中追求刺激感的人才會面臨的問題。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "反而是與不習慣戰鬥的人更切身相關的問題。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "你的意思是？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "之前我也提到過銃比其他武器更容易操作的事對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "當然，我記得喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "使用銃的時候不需要力量，只要經過少許訓練，便能發揮出相當程度的殺傷力。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "重點就是，即使是不習慣戰鬥的人只要拿到銃也能馬上成為即戰力。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "但是，就如同我剛才說的，銃不像其他武器可以帶來刺激感……打倒敵人的真實感非常薄弱。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "而打倒敵人的真實感薄弱，就代表對戰鬥的恐懼感同樣低下。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "……是嗎？喬想說的事情，我也漸漸能明白了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "所謂的戰鬥，是必須讓人恐懼的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0065.wav"], "content": "但是，若把銃交給人們廣泛流傳，那覺得戰鬥恐怖的感覺，會不會也因此而消失呢……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "那就是喬感到不安的真正原因嗎……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "有刺激感的戰鬥，是要讓每個正在戰鬥的人互相都感到恐懼才能成立。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "銃雖是強大的武器，但正因它強大，所以容易使人傲慢，令恐懼感麻痺……說得具體點，就是那種戰鬥沒有靈魂。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "沒有靈魂的戰鬥，就只會帶來空虛感而已……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "喬……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "哈，我也真是糊塗了。看來拿到這玩意時感受到的可能性，到頭來也不過是場誤會而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "這把銃就還給你吧。我說過的話，也麻煩轉告給你姊姊了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "我知道了。這把銃，我就趕在今天內讓人駕車送還給謝斯姊姊吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "喬所提到的那些須要留意的事項，我也會好好轉達的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "嗯，麻煩你啦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "「銃」嗎……哼，這看來能派上用場。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110003023, "title": "不足之物"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0075.wav"], "content": "喬，不好了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "怎麼啦，尤蒂爾？看你這麼驚慌失措……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "運送銃的馬車似乎遭到來路不明的盜賊襲擊。車夫雖然是逃過了一劫……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "但銃被奪走了……是嗎？我知道了。我也來幫忙搜索奪走銃的盜賊吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "太感謝了。我這就到香捷里亞去，向謝斯姊姊把事情說明清楚。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "喬就去追查奪走銃的盜賊吧。保險起見，我就把備用的銃交給你了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "但是，我已經對銃……不，現在不是說這種話的時候呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "關於那個賊人的下落，已經有眉目了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "馬車被襲擊的位置是在伊剛山地的南方，所以──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0053.wav"], "content": "找到你了……！把「銃」奪走的盜賊，就是你對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "──！？你是米格爾！？怎麼會……不可能有這種事的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "沒錯，米格爾不可能還活著。他已經因為在決鬥中敗給你而死去了。喬，是你殺了我的弟弟！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "奪走銃的男子", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "弟弟！？那麼，你就是米格爾的……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "我是拉蒙……那個賭上了弓箭世界最強男人的挑戰權而與你一戰的，你的宿敵米格爾──我就是他的哥哥。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "沒想到他居然有個長得一模一樣的哥哥……我一次也沒聽他本人說過。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "哼，這也難怪。畢竟他對我這個雙胞胎哥哥，似乎是抱持著自卑感。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "你奪走銃，是為了與我戰鬥……這是打算要憑弔你的弟弟嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "沒錯，這就是為了弟弟的復仇！你就與我一戰，然後慘死吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "唔，好快！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "嘖，被擦到了嗎！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0044.wav"], "content": "怎麼啦！為什麼不用銃反擊！還是說，你比較想要就這樣不抵抗，直接讓我把你殺了！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "那麼我就如你所願，一擊打穿你的心臟吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0057.wav"], "content": "休想！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "唔，居然有同伴在！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾，你什麼時候來的！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "去完香捷里亞之後，我就追在喬後面趕過來了。比起這些，喬你趕快使用銃吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "你曾經說過銃裡面沒有靈魂，但事情不應該是這樣的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "這是什麼意思？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "你只是沒有遇到能夠一戰的對手而已。只是還沒遇到可以讓你的靈魂亢奮、感受到恐懼心情的對手罷了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "但是，現在有個符合條件的對手了。兩者都是使用銃，並且都抱持著同樣的恐懼戰鬥……沒錯吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "……呵，你說得沒錯。現在我的眼前，有一個讓我須要賭上靈魂一戰的對手……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "這子彈之中是否寄宿著靈魂，就用這場決鬥來見真章吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "那麼，我……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "嗯，抱歉了。麻煩你好好看著這場決鬥，直到最後一刻。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "我知道了。那接下來就交給喬了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "讓你久等了。那麼，我們就來做個了斷吧。用銃進行速射對決，沒問題吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "當然，比速度的話，不管用銃還是弓箭，我都有信心能不輸給任何人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "跟你弟弟米格爾比也是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "弟弟的弓術可是我教他的。雖然他是弓術的天才，但會有狀況不佳的時候，缺乏安定性。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "雖然我與弟弟的實力不相上下……但如果他能發揮本領，我相信將來有潛力會超越我，並成為世界第一！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "如果我弟弟能發揮出真正的本事，像你這種角色根本不可能贏過他。我會打倒你，證明我說的話沒錯……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "……原來如此。你要說的我都懂了。你的實力與米格爾相當，從剛才的射擊就能看出來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "但是，你有沒有辦法擊敗我，那就要等到試過了才知道喔！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "哼，馬上就會分曉。我會讓你明白……就用停在那岩石上的鳥起飛的瞬間作為開戰的信號，沒問題吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0072.wav"], "content": "好啊。我早就已經準備好了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "可別後悔了…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "（贏了！是我比較快──！？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "唔啊啊啊！？我的手！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "哼，速射對決是我贏了呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0065.wav"], "content": "為什麼，伸手舉起銃的動作明明是我先完成的才對啊……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "這場對決沒有任何心機與把戲，單純就只是我比較強而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "但是，真要說的話，大概就是使用銃的熟練度……在這東西上灌注了多少靈魂的差異吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0029.wav"], "content": "……是你贏了，殺了我吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "我拒絕。我可不喜歡被誰命令。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120085_story/VO_CHR_120085_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "你這麼做要付出很高的代價喔。只要你一天不殺了我，我就一定會再次出現在你面前……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120085_01.png", "speakerName": "拉蒙", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "正合我意。你就隨時放馬過來吧。但如果你還是被恨意給沖昏頭的話，不管來幾次都是無謂的喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "不清醒的人擊出的子彈可打不到我。想復仇就得冷靜，這可是江湖規矩……你就先讓頭腦清醒過了再來找我吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_01.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110003024, "title": "雙銃對決"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "喂～喬！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "原來你在這種地方啊。我找你好久了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "怎麼了，又有載著銃的馬車被盜賊襲擊了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不是啦，再怎麼樣我也不會讓這種事情重蹈覆轍好嗎。這次是有別的事啦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "喬之前提出的對於銃的疑慮，因為各種原因，我到現在都還沒把謝斯姊姊的答覆轉達給你。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "所以是專程跑來告訴我的嗎？你也真是一板一眼的傢伙耶。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "然後呢？你的姊姊說了什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "明確說來，喬所顧忌的事情，謝斯姊姊也已經知道了喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "她原本就沒打算把銃托付給不了解戰鬥有多可怕的人……把銃交給我們前她就已經心裡有數了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "你相當受到她的信賴嘛。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "畢竟是謝斯姊姊，比起信賴，或許比較該理解成不管怎樣都在她的計算之中吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "確實，她感覺就是會把與奪走銃的盜賊戰鬥這種事當成是雙銃對決的實驗樣本呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "而那個謝斯姊姊，有個禮物要送給喬。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "禮物？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "作為幫忙試用銃的回禮……來，收下這個吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1001.wav"], "content": "這次的已經不是實驗品了。而是參考喬的建議所製成的完成品──是專屬於喬的銃。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "那個啊，尤蒂爾……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "銃裡沒有靈魂，所以無法進行充滿刺激感的戰鬥……我之前是這麼說的，對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1015.wav"], "content": "嗯，我記得喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "但是，那是我的誤解。銃裡也有靈魂……只是它需要的練習比較少，所以比較難察覺。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "我在之前的決鬥中，深刻地感受到靈魂──感受到刺激。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "我的銃裡寄宿著靈魂。當時分出勝負的關鍵，就在於我與他對銃注入靈魂的差異。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "靈魂的差異……你是指技術的差別嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "全部都是。不論是技術或是意志，賭在那場戰鬥中的全部都是靈魂。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "單純以技術來說的話，我與拉蒙並沒有多少差別。但對銃付出的心思，就天差地遠了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "就算僅以短暫的訓練就能使用銃，但只要其中沒有靈魂就一點也不可怕。正所謂不足為懼的敵人吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "但多虧他，讓我發現到了。只要是注入靈魂的銃，應該就能讓我充分品味一直在追尋的刺激感……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "那麼……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "沒錯，這把銃……我會把它當作我的新搭檔，心懷感激地使用的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110003_story/VO_CHR_110003_STORY_0068.wav"], "content": "哼，今天起我就是「手持光耀銃的男人」啦！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110003_02.png", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110003025, "title": "新的搭檔"}]